  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Algor PEW PEW is the first game from Algorhythm Project which will bring you a new experience in rogue-lite bullet-hell survival genre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599700/extras/1c3ef6ba1c322102178e6c2bd3300aa4.avif?t=1727616658\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599700/extras_big/1c3ef6ba1c322102178e6c2bd3300aa4.avif?t=1727616658 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Mechanics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Music X Survival</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy your favourite songs from Algorhythm Project in 8-bit version and survive until the last song however, the more intense the song is, the stronger enemies are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Medley mode</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick the songs, Create a playlist and dive to the stage with your songs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own stage and beat your own challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Party member</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you rescue an ARP, he/she will grant you his/her power and fight along side you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599700/extras/37c0ecc8694dbf613f0c1f0a86f51ddd.avif?t=1727616658\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Algor PEW PEW is the first game from Algorhythm Project which will bring you a new experience in rogue-lite bullet-hell survival genre.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599700/extras/1c3ef6ba1c322102178e6c2bd3300aa4.avif?t=1727616658\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599700/extras_big/1c3ef6ba1c322102178e6c2bd3300aa4.avif?t=1727616658 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Mechanics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Music X Survival</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy your favourite songs from Algorhythm Project in 8-bit version and survive until the last song however, the more intense the song is, the stronger enemies are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Medley mode</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick the songs, Create a playlist and dive to the stage with your songs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own stage and beat your own challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Party member</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you rescue an ARP, he/she will grant you his/her power and fight along side you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2599700/extras/37c0ecc8694dbf613f0c1f0a86f51ddd.avif?t=1727616658\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p>",
